Advancement Screenshot.name: Advancement Screenshot
Advancement Screenshot.summary: [Client] Takes a screenshot every time an advancement is achieved. Document your progress!

All Loot Drops.name: All Loot Drops
All Loot Drops.summary: Living entities always drop all their possible loot in a configurable amount, looting enchant supported.

Altered Damage.name: Altered Damage
Altered Damage.summary: Alters damage taken and dealt by players and other entities with a modifier.

Always a Wither Skull.name: Always a Wither Skull
Always a Wither Skull.summary: A drag-and-drop mod which makes wither skeletons always drop their skull on death.

Areas.name: Areas
Areas.summary: Create custom named regions/towns/zones with a radius using signs, with join/leave messages via GUI.

Automatic Doors.name: Automatic Doors
Automatic Doors.summary: Automatically opens doors around the player and closes them with a configurable delay.

Bamboo Spreads.name: Bamboo Spreads
Bamboo Spreads.summary: Bamboo has a chance to create a new chute/sapling on a nearby block when growing.

Better Beacon Placement.name: Better Beacon Placement
Better Beacon Placement.summary: Easily place beacon bases by right-clicking the beacon with a mineral block plus other tweaks.

Better Conduit Placement.name: Better Conduit Placement
Better Conduit Placement.summary: Place conduits in front, makes placing conduit prismarine blocks easier and other tweaks.

Better Spawner Control.name: Better Spawner Control
Better Spawner Control.summary: A drag-and-drop mod which disables mob spawners whenever they are surrounded by 5 torches.

Bigger Sponge Absorption Radius.name: Bigger Sponge Absorption Radius
Bigger Sponge Absorption Radius.summary: Each extra sponge block placed next to one another increases the water absorption radius.

Bottle Your Xp.name: Bottle Your Xp
Bottle Your Xp.summary: Allows the creation of experience bottles (bottles o' enchanting) from your own gathered xp.

Breedable Killer Rabbit.name: Breedable Killer Rabbit
Breedable Killer Rabbit.summary: Makes the killer rabbit/bunny tamable and available by breeding.

Campfire Spawn and Tweaks.name: Campfire Spawn and Tweaks
Campfire Spawn and Tweaks.summary: Respawn interdimensionally with short fire resistance inside a preferred campfire with altered block mechanics. Place unlit, lighting it will create a home camp spawn point. Remove waterlogging.

Collective.name: Collective
Collective.summary: Collective is a shared library with common code for all of Serilum's mods.

Conduits Prevent Drowned.name: Conduits Prevent Drowned
Conduits Prevent Drowned.summary: Disables drowned zombie spawns around the player when the conduit effect is active.

Configurable Despawn Timer.name: Configurable Despawn Timer
Configurable Despawn Timer.summary: Allows items to remain on the ground longer or shorter than the default lifespan.

Configurable Extra Mob Drops.name: Configurable Extra Mob Drops
Configurable Extra Mob Drops.summary: Add any extra item drops to entities via commands and config, drop chance supported.

Configurable Mob Potion Effects.name: Configurable Mob Potion Effects
Configurable Mob Potion Effects.summary: Set potion effects for all living entities to have permanently and to inflict on targets.

Creative Block Replacer.name: Creative Block Replacer
Creative Block Replacer.summary: Allows easy switching in between placing and replacing blocks in creative mode.

Crying Ghasts.name: Crying Ghasts
Crying Ghasts.summary: Ghasts drop their tears periodically when a player is close, allowing sustainable farming.

Cycle Paintings.name: Cycle Paintings
Cycle Paintings.summary: Easily cycle through placed paintings by right-clicking them with a painting in hand.

Death Backup.name: Death Backup
Death Backup.summary: Creates back-ups from the inventory of players before death, which can be loaded via commands.

Despawning Eggs Hatch.name: Despawning Eggs Hatch
Despawning Eggs Hatch.summary: Allows chicken eggs on hay blocks to hatch safely into chicks just before they despawn.

Difficulty Lock.name: Difficulty Lock
Difficulty Lock.summary: Sets the difficulty to peaceful/easy/normal/hard in any (new) world, optionally locked.

Dismount Entity.name: Dismount Entity
Dismount Entity.summary: Allows players to dismount/remove/exit entities/mobs from mounted entities without breaking them.

Double Doors.name: Double Doors
Double Doors.summary: Adds the ability for identical double doors, trapdoors and fence gates to be opened simultaneously.

Dragon Drops Elytra.name: Dragon Drops Elytra
Dragon Drops Elytra.summary: A minimalistic mod that makes the Ender Dragon drop an elytra on death.

Easy Elytra Takeoff.name: Easy Elytra Takeoff
Easy Elytra Takeoff.summary: Allows easy takeoff by elytra/colytra with a firework from the ground without an awkward jump.

Edibles.name: Edibles
Edibles.summary: Makes lots of ingredients edible, after which the player receives a short status effect. Allows eating blaze powder, glowstone dust, magma cream, sugar, ghast tear, phantom membrane and rabbit's foot.

Enchanting Commands.name: Enchanting Commands
Enchanting Commands.summary: Allows for easy creation of enchanted items via commands with levels above the default limit.

End Portal Recipe.name: End Portal Recipe
End Portal Recipe.summary: Makes the end portal craftable, movable and available in survival plus other tweaks for vanilla.

Entity Information.name: Entity Information
Entity Information.summary: Displays entity information on hit with the Information Stick. Useful for debugging and developing.

Eroding Stone Entities.name: Eroding Stone Entities
Eroding Stone Entities.summary: Stone-type block entities left in flowing water for some time turn into clay and sand.

Extended Bone Meal.name: Extended Bone Meal
Extended Bone Meal.summary: Extends bonemeal behaviour. Instant grow with sneak, grow netherwart+cacti+sugarcane and other tweaks.

Extended Creative Inventory.name: Extended Creative Inventory
Extended Creative Inventory.summary: Adds all items which by default aren't in the creative inventory to a custom tab.

Extract Poison.name: Extract Poison
Extract Poison.summary: Allows the extraction of poison from cave spiders, pufferfish and bees with an empty bottle.

Fall Through Slime.name: Fall Through Slime
Fall Through Slime.summary: Slime blocks no longer support your weight when standing still, and you'll slowly fall through.

Fish On The Line.name: Fish On The Line
Fish On The Line.summary: Rings a bell held in your offhand when something's nibbling on the line while fishing.

Fire Spread Tweaks.name: Fire Spread Tweaks
Fire Spread Tweaks.summary: Disables the default firespread and makes fire go out after a configurable delay.

First Join Message.name: First Join Message
First Join Message.summary: Sends players who join a world for the first time a configurable message.

Fixed Anvil Repair Cost.name: Fixed Anvil Repair Cost
Fixed Anvil Repair Cost.summary: Patches the anvil to set the default level cost, material cost and percentage repaired.

Full Brightness Toggle.name: Full Brightness Toggle
Full Brightness Toggle.summary: [Client] Press G to instantly toggle the brightness/gamma in-game to maximum and get night vision.

Giant Spawn.name: Giant Spawn
Giant Spawn.summary: Allows giants to spawn naturally with custom AI (based on zombies) and other tweaks.

Grass Seeds.name: Grass Seeds
Grass Seeds.summary: Allows players to use normal seeds to transform dirt into (tall) grass.

Grindstone Sharper Tools.name: Grindstone Sharper Tools
Grindstone Sharper Tools.summary: The grindstone (wet stone) can temporarily increase the damage of tools used on it.

GUI Clock.name: GUI Clock
GUI Clock.summary: [Client] Shows the time/days played in the GUI/HUD with a clock in the inventory.

GUI Compass.name: GUI Compass
GUI Compass.summary: [Client] Shows direction and coordinates in the GUI/HUD with a compass in the inventory.

GUI Followers.name: GUI Followers
GUI Followers.summary: [Client] Shows a list in the GUI/HUD with information on all tamed non-sitting followers around.

Hand Over Your Items.name: Hand Over Your Items
Hand Over Your Items.summary: Adds to ability for in-game players to give each other itemstacks without dropping/tossing them.

Healing Campfire.name: Healing Campfire
Healing Campfire.summary: Creates an area around the (soul) campfire where players and passive mobs receive regeneration.

Healing Soup.name: Healing Soup
Healing Soup.summary: [PvP Mod] Soup heals hearts. Adds recipes for chocolate milk, cactus soup and mushroom stew.

Hidden Recipe Book.name: Hidden Recipe Book
Hidden Recipe Book.summary: [Client] Toggle the visiblity of the recipe book button by hotkey in crafting GUI screens.

Hide Hands.name: Hide Hands
Hide Hands.summary: [Client] Hide your offhand and/or main hand in first person, optionally while holding specific items like a torch, totem of undying or a shield.

Humbling Bundle.name: Humbling Bundle
Humbling Bundle.summary: Doubles all entity loot, to increase the speed of early game progress and late-game grinds. Inspired by the identically titled item in the binding of Isaac.

Husk Spawn.name: Husk Spawn
Husk Spawn.summary: Adds a chance for husks to spawn naturally everywhere in place of a zombie.

Ice Prevents Crop Growth.name: Ice Prevents Crop Growth
Ice Prevents Crop Growth.summary: Crops growing with ice underneath will never mature to the next stage, for design purposes.

Infinite Trading.name: Infinite Trading
Infinite Trading.summary: Prevents villager trades from locking up, making them always available. The wandering trader is supported.

Inventory Totem.name: Inventory Totem
Inventory Totem.summary: Makes the totem of undying effect work when it's anywhere in the inventory.

Just Mob Heads.name: Just Mob Heads
Just Mob Heads.summary: Adds a configurable chance for mobs to drop their head, using vanilla resources only.

Just Player Heads.name: Just Player Heads
Just Player Heads.summary: Allows the collection of player heads via command or death event. All heads are generated similar to a mob head via texture-data, lag free.

Kelp Fertilizer.name: Kelp Fertilizer
Kelp Fertilizer.summary: Kelp seaweed naturally filters sea water for rich nutrients. Kelp now works like bone meal.

Milk All The Mobs.name: Milk All The Mobs
Milk All The Mobs.summary: Allows sheep, llamas, pigs, donkeys, horses and mules to produce a bucket of milk.

Mineral Chance.name: Mineral Chance
Mineral Chance.summary: Players sometimes find a mineral inside stone-type blocks when mining in the overworld and nether.

Mooshroom Spawn.name: Mooshroom Spawn
Mooshroom Spawn.summary: Adds a chance for mooshrooms to spawn naturally everywhere in place of a cow.

Mooshroom Tweaks.name: Mooshroom Tweaks
Mooshroom Tweaks.summary: A 1.14+ minimalistic configurable mod that allows both red and brown mooshrooms to spawn naturally.

More Zombie Villagers.name: More Zombie Villagers
More Zombie Villagers.summary: Allows changing the default chance a zombie spawns as the villager variant.

Move Boats.name: Move Boats
Move Boats.summary: Allows players to easily move boats without breaking them by holding right click.

Move Minecarts.name: Move Minecarts
Move Minecarts.summary: Allows players to easily pick up and move minecarts without breaking them by holding right click.

Name Tag Tweaks.name: Name Tag Tweaks
Name Tag Tweaks.summary: Adds name tag crafting recipe, /nametag command, and named entities drop a nametag on death.

Naturally Charged Creepers.name: Naturally Charged Creepers
Naturally Charged Creepers.summary: Allows creepers to spawn charged in order to increase the game's difficulty.

Nether Portal Spread.name: Nether Portal Spread
Nether Portal Spread.summary: Spreads (nether) blocks to the overworld around nether and immersive portals in a configurable radius.

No Hostiles Around Campfire.name: No Hostiles Around Campfire
No Hostiles Around Campfire.summary: Prevents hostile mob spawns and burns them around the (soul) campfire in a configurable radius.

Nutritious Milk.name: Nutritious Milk
Nutritious Milk.summary: Adds a nutritious value to milk, filling up the food bar and saturation when consumed.

Omega Mute.name: Omega Mute
Omega Mute.summary: [Client] The only mod you'll need to have full control over individual in-game sound.

Paper Books.name: Paper Books
Paper Books.summary: Allows the creation of books with 9 paper.

Passive Endermen.name: Passive Endermen
Passive Endermen.summary: Configurably prevent an enderman from teleporting, placing/picking up blocks (griefing) and attacking when looked at.

Passive Shield.name: Passive Shield
Passive Shield.summary: The shield is hidden and provides protection passively when held idle in the offhand.

Pet Names.name: Pet Names
Pet Names.summary: Gives tamable baby animals a pre-defined name. For wolves, cats, horses, donkeys, mules and llamas.

Placeable Blaze Rods.name: Placeable Blaze Rods
Placeable Blaze Rods.summary: Makes blaze rods placeable as a custom block in the world, similar to end rods.

Player Death Kick.name: Player Death Kick
Player Death Kick.summary: Kicks players on death with a customizable disconnect message.

Player Tracking.name: Player Tracking
Player Tracking.summary: A 1.7 and 1.12+ PvP Mod. Allows the tracking of players via special trackers.

Player Tracking Compass.name: Player Tracking Compass
Player Tracking Compass.summary: [PvP Mod] Adds a Tracking Compass, which tracks the nearest player's location on right click.

Quick Paths.name: Quick Paths
Quick Paths.summary: Create long paths instantly by setting a start and end point.

Rain Be Gone Ritual.name: Rain Be Gone Ritual
Rain Be Gone Ritual.summary: Adds the ability to stop the rain via a multi-block structure ritual in survival mode.

Random Bone Meal Flowers.name: Random Bone Meal Flowers
Random Bone Meal Flowers.summary: Randomizes the flowers spawned by bonemeal, allowing all (modded) types to spawn everywhere.

Random Mob Effects.name: Random Mob Effects
Random Mob Effects.summary: Randomly assign a (modded) potion effect to all hostile mobs in the world.

Random Sheep Colours.name: Random Sheep Colours
Random Sheep Colours.summary: Gives new sheep spawns a random wool/fleece color based on a configurable list.

Random Shulker Colours.name: Random Shulker Colours
Random Shulker Colours.summary: Gives new shulker spawns a random shell color based on a configurable list.

Random Village Names.name: Random Village Names
Random Village Names.summary: All villages receive a randomized name, shown in the GUI via the Areas mod.

Realistic Bees.name: Realistic Bees
Realistic Bees.summary: Makes bee behaviour more realistic. Losing their stinger is fatal, bigger group spawns and more.

Recast.name: Recast
Recast.summary: Automatically re-casts the fishing rod line for a player when an item is caught.

Recipe Commands.name: Recipe Commands
Recipe Commands.summary: Adds the ability to receive the pattern and ingredients of any item recipe via chat.

Replanting Crops.name: Replanting Crops
Replanting Crops.summary: Automatically replants/replaces/reseeds crops harvested with a hoe by using the drops. Works with wheat, carrots, potatoes, beetroots, netherwart and cocoa beans.

Respawn Delay.name: Respawn Delay
Respawn Delay.summary: [PvP Mod] Players enter spectator mode on death for a configurable amount of time.

Respawning Shulkers.name: Respawning Shulkers
Respawning Shulkers.summary: Shulkers will respawn at their death location after a configurable delay, farm shells sustainably.

Save and Load Inventories.name: Save and Load Inventories
Save and Load Inventories.summary: Save and load player inventories or preset kits to self and others by using commands.

Scaffolding Drops Nearby.name: Scaffolding Drops Nearby
Scaffolding Drops Nearby.summary: When breaking a scaffolding block, all chained blocks will drop at the first block's position.

Set World Spawn Point.name: Set World Spawn Point
Set World Spawn Point.summary: Allows setting an exact custom spawn point for (newly) created worlds and spawn tweaks.

Shulker Drops Two.name: Shulker Drops Two
Shulker Drops Two.summary: Allows Shulkers to drop two or more shells and ignore their default drop chance.

Silence Mobs.name: Silence Mobs
Silence Mobs.summary: Adds the functionality to silence or mute a mob or villager with The Silence Stick.

Skeleton Horse Spawn.name: Skeleton Horse Spawn
Skeleton Horse Spawn.summary: Allows skeleton horses to spawn naturally with a skeleton riding it and other tweaks.

Sleep Sooner.name: Sleep Sooner
Sleep Sooner.summary: Also Sleep Later! Make players go to bed at a different time.

Smaller Nether Portals.name: Smaller Nether Portals
Smaller Nether Portals.summary: Allows the creation of smaller nether portals, specifically 1x2, 1x3 and 2x2.

Snowballs Freeze Mobs.name: Snowballs Freeze Mobs
Snowballs Freeze Mobs.summary: Hitting mobs with a snowball will freeze them for a configurable amount of time.

Softer Hay Bales.name: Softer Hay Bales
Softer Hay Bales.summary: Makes hay bales negate fall damage entirely, Assassin's Creed style.

Spiders Produce Webs.name: Spiders Produce Webs
Spiders Produce Webs.summary: Spiders and cave spiders can periodically produce a cobweb/spiderweb when a player is close.

Stack Refill.name: Stack Refill
Stack Refill.summary: Automatically refills the player's hand when using the final item if a replacement exists.

Starter Kit.name: Starter Kit
Starter Kit.summary: Gives players joining the world for the first time configurable starter gear and items which overwrites the initial inventory.

Stray Spawn.name: Stray Spawn
Stray Spawn.summary: Adds a chance for strays to spawn naturally everywhere in place of a skeleton.

Superflat World No Slimes.name: Superflat World No Slimes
Superflat World No Slimes.summary: Removes those pesky slimes when you're trying to be creative in a superflat world.

The Vanilla Experience.name: The Vanilla Experience (Mod)
The Vanilla Experience.summary: A mod mirror of the identically named modpack. Includes 104 of Serilum's mods bundled together.

TNT Breaks Bedrock.name: TNT Breaks Bedrock
TNT Breaks Bedrock.summary: Allows TNT to break bedrock. Now you've finally got easy access to the nether roof.

Trample Everything.name: Trample Everything
Trample Everything.summary: A highly configurable mod which makes players trample everything, not just crops.

Transcending Trident.name: Transcending Trident
Transcending Trident.summary: Improves the vanilla trident. Hold a water bucket to use a more powerful riptide anywhere.

Tree Harvester.name: Tree Harvester
Tree Harvester.summary: Harvest trees instantly by chopping down the bottom. With fast leaf decay and sapling replacement.

Underwater Enchanting.name: Underwater Enchanting
Underwater Enchanting.summary: Allows the use of the enchantment table under water with maximum levels via bookshelves.

Village Spawn Point.name: Village Spawn Point
Village Spawn Point.summary: Sets the spawn point in a newly generated world to the center of a village.

Village Bell Recipe.name: Village Bell Recipe
Village Bell Recipe.summary: Makes the bell item craftable via a recipe with stone, logs and a golden block.

Villager Death Messages.name: Villager Death Messages
Villager Death Messages.summary: Broadcasts an informational death message whenever a villager passes away.

Villager Names.name: Villager Names
Villager Names.summary: A minimalistic mod which gives all unnamed (modded) villagers a pre-defined or custom name.

Vote Command.name: Vote Command
Vote Command.summary: [Server] Adds a configurable /vote command which tells players how and where to vote.

Weaker Spiderwebs.name: Weaker Spiderwebs
Weaker Spiderwebs.summary: Breaks spider webs/cobwebs with a configurable delay when walking through.

Wool Tweaks.name: Wool Tweaks
Wool Tweaks.summary: Makes various changes to wool-type block recipes, string conversion and the process of dyeing them.

World Border.name: World Border
World Border.summary: Allows the creation of a configurable world border for each dimension, limiting the world size.

Zombie Horse Spawn.name: Zombie Horse Spawn
Zombie Horse Spawn.summary: Allows zombie horses to spawn with a zombie riding it and other tweaks.

Zombie Proof Doors.name: Zombie Proof Doors
Zombie Proof Doors.summary: Prevents zombies from targeting and breaking down doors.

Zombie Villagers From Spawner.name: Zombie Villagers From Spawner
Zombie Villagers From Spawner.summary: Puts back the ability for zombie spawners to spawn the villager variant, removed in 1.11.
